"title": "5135: blindness, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5135",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An inability or unwillingness to perceive the truth of the gospel.</p>\n<h2>Unbelievers are spiritually blind</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:6-Ps92:7\">PSA 92:6–92:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:19\">PRO 4:19</a>ISA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov44:9\">44:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:18-Isa44:19\">ISA 44:18–44:19</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:2\">EZK 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic13:13-Mic13:15\">13:13–13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:10\">LUK 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:16\">MAT 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25\">LUK 24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:5\">JHN 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:40-John9:41\">JHN 9:40–9:41</a> <em>the spiritual blindness of the Pharisees</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:11\">ROM 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:23\">1CO 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24\">1CO 14:24</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual blindness is a result of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:14\">LAM 4:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:17\">ZEP 1:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:32\">MRK 9:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:34\">LUK 18:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19-John3:20\">JHN 3:19–3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:39-John12:40\">JHN 12:39–12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:19\">EPH 4:17–4:19</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of spiritual blindness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:18–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:28-Deut28:29\">DEU 28:28–28:29</a> <em>lack of success, oppression and robbery</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:5\">PSA 82:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:25\">ISA 42:25</a> <em>the violence of war</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:10\">ISA 59:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:14\">LAM 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:23\">MAT 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:26-Acts28:27\">ACT 28:26–28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:61\">1JN 1:61</a>JN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:9\">2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:11\">1JN 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>The removal of spiritual blindness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:4\">NUM 24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:17</a> <em>Elisha asks the LORD to open his servant's eyes</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:18\">PSA 119:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:8\">PSA 146:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:3\">ISA 32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:5\">ISA 35:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:16-Isa42:18\">ISA 42:16–42:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:31\">LUK 24:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3\">JHN 3:3</a> <em>No-one can see the kingdom of God without being born again</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a> <em>Jesus Christ is the light of the world</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:39\">JHN 9:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:18\">ACT 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:16\">2CO 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">EPH 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>The spiritual blindness of Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:3\">ISA 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:4\">DEU 29:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:28\">DEU 32:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:10\">ISA 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:21\">JER 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:7-Rom11:8\">ROM 11:7–11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25\">ROM 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14-2Cor3:15\">2CO 3:14–3:15</a></p>\n<h2>The spiritual blindness of leaders</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:14\">MAT 15:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:9-Isa29:12\">ISA 29:9–29:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:10\">ISA 56:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:16-Matt23:19\">MAT 23:16–23:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:24-Matt23:26\">MAT 23:24–23:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:39\">LUK 6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:10\">JHN 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:27\">JHN 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:40-John9:41\">JHN 9:40–9:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:6\">JHN 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:19-Rom2:21\">ROM 2:19–2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:12\">2PE 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>The spiritual blindness of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:3\">JOB 42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:8\">DAN 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:16\">MAT 15:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:18\">MRK 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:9\">MAT 16:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:21\">MRK 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:50\">LUK 2:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:45\">LUK 9:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25\">LUK 24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:16\">JHN 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:9\">2PE 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>The spiritual blindness of a church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17-Rev3:18\">REV 3:17–3:18</a></strong></p>",
